schema.title: buf.plugin.yaml
schema.description: A `buf.plugin.yaml` file captures metadata about the plugin. It includes mandatory and optional fields that are displayed on the individual plugin page and the BSR plugin homepage at https://buf.build/plugins.

version.description: The YAML configuration version, must be `v1`.

plugin_version.description: The plugin version with format`v{semver}`, the `v` prefix is required and the version must be valid [semantic versioning](https://semver.org/).

source_url.description: URL to the source code of the Protobuf plugin.

output_languages.description: The output language types generated by the plugin. See the PluginLanguage enum for existing languages. Open a GitHub issue in the Buf CLI (https://github.com/bufbuild/buf) if the output language isn't found for a plugin.

spdx_license_id.description: The license id for the plugin from https://spdx.org/licenses.

integration_guide_url.description: The URL to the integration guide for the plugin.

deps.description: A list of dependencies on other plugins used by Generated SDKs.

plugin.description: The reference to the plugin dependency with format `{name}:{plugin_version}`.

revision.description: If specified, the dependency will be to a specific version of a plugin. It is recommended to leave this off (the plugin will depend on the latest revision at time of publishing).

registry.description: Configuration to enable a plugin for use with Generated SDKs.

opts.description: Options supplied to the plugin when generating code for the SDK.

go.description: Generated SDK configuration for a Go plugin.

min_version.description: The minimum Go version required by the plugin (e.g. `1.19`), used as the go directive in the `go.mod` file. See https://go.dev/ref/mod#go-mod-file-go.

deps.description: A list of Go module requirements. Each requirement corresponds to a require directive in the `go.mod` file. See https://go.dev/ref/mod#go-mod-file-require.

npm.description: Generated SDK configuration for a JavaScript/TypeScript plugin.

rewrite_import_path_suffix.description: The suffix used in the generated files and their imported dependencies (supported by @bufbuild/protoplugin (https://www.npmjs.com/package/@bufbuild/protoplugin) plugins).

deps.description: NPM package dependencies for the Generated SDK.

package.description: The name of the NPM package dependency.

version.description: The version of the NPM package dependency (see https://docs.npmjs.com/about-semantic-versioning#using-semantic-versioning-to-specify-update-types-your-package-can-accept for more details).

maven.description: Generated SDK configuration for a Java/Kotlin plugin.

deps.description: Runtime dependencies of the generated Java/Kotlin code (in GAV format).

name.description: The name of the additional runtime. The only known name at this time is `lite` for Protobuf lite runtime support.

deps.description: Dependencies for the runtime. These override `registry -> maven -> deps` if specified.

opts.description: Plugin options for the additional runtime.

python.description: Generated SDK configuration for a Python plugin.

deps.description: Runtime dependencies of the generated code.

requires_python.description: Specifies the `Requires-Python` of the generated package.

swift.description: Generated SDK configuration for a Swift plugin.

swift_versions.description: Versions of Swift the package supports.

cargo.description: Generated SDK configuration for a Rust plugin.

rust_version.description: The rust-version set for the generated crate.

deps.description: Crates.io dependencies for the Generated SDK.

req.description: The version request of the dependency.

default_features.description: Whether or not to enable default features for the dependency.

features.description: The features to enable for the dependency.

nuget.description: Generated SDK configuration for a C# plugin.

target_frameworks.description: The target frameworks the generated package supports.

deps.description: nuget.org dependencies for the Generated SDK.

name.description: The package ID of the dependency.

version.description: The version range of the dependency.

target_frameworks.description: The target frameworks the dependency applies to.

cmake.description: Generated SDK configuration for a CMake plugin.
